      },
      "date": "2013-04-12 00:46:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1c4b6304-a304-11e2-a7df-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  3 tests failed: sanity-quota, recovery-small, replay-single.",
